===Pronunciation===
swĕt, /swɛt/, /swEt/

=== Noun ===
'''sweat''' (''[[uncountable]]'')

#(''physiology'') [[Fluid]] that exits the [[body]] though [[pore]]s in the [[skin]] usually due to [[physical]] [[stress]] and/or [[high]] [[temperature]] for the purpose of regulating body temperature and removing certain compounds from the [[circulation]].
#(''in plural'' '''sweats'''; ''informal'') A [[sweatsuit]].

====Synonyms====
*(''fluid that exits the body through pores''): [[perspiration]]
*(''sweatsuit''): [[sweatsuit]]

